**The Petite Hidden Halo Solitaire** with 81 reviews is the most field-tested solitaire setting for pear diamonds on Blue Nile. The hidden halo sits beneath the center stone, adding a ring of accent diamonds that is visible from the side and catches light from below the stone — without framing the top face of the pear. From above, it reads as a clean solitaire. From the side and profile, there is extra sparkle. This is the correct setting for buyers who want solitaire aesthetics with hidden detail.

